ast.name: TV•remote
ast.comment:
App using JointSpace API to remote control Philips TV using WiFi.

Update adds stationdisplay,
new buttons, better colors in lightmode.

Wifi connection to TV required. Should work with Philips 2k9 models (8000-9000 range, number ending with a 4) 2K10 models(7000-9000 range, number ending with a 5)
2k11 models xxPFL5xx6-xxPFL9xx6.

app.comment:
App using JointSpace API to remote control Philips TV, using WiFi. Update fixes stationdisplay bug. New buttons, better colors in lightmode. Wifi connection to TV required. Should work with Philips 2k9 models (8000-9000 range, number ending with a 4) 2K10 models(7000-9000 range, number ending with a 5) 2k11 models xxPFL5xx6-xxPFL9xx6.
Requieres TD native Client.
